	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b>Re: random MML tools discussion</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I have used ppMCK, and I wrote AmigaMML (so if you have questions about it, you can ask me).<br /><br />One other MML compiler I have heard of is SakuraMML, which outputs MIDI. However, it is in Japanese (and I am not very good at Japanese).<br /><br />There is also CsoundMML, which produces a <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Csound" class="postlink">Csound</a> numeric score.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


