	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I edited the thread, so hopefully that'll suffice.<br />Here's my MML. It's nothing but a test just to make sure stuff works. In its current state it seems to work fine, but I don't know how to use the effects/other envelopes.<br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">#EXTENDED 1<br />#TITLE test<br />#DIVISIONS 16<br />#SPEED 6<br />#SIGNATURE 4,4<br />#TEMPO 120<br />@0 &quot;test.xi&quot;<br /><br />A @0 o4 l8 c e g e c4</div><br />Let me know if I'm doing anything that looks weird; I'm pretty new to tracking in general so even though it's easier for me to work through it in text, I'm not used to some of the concepts.<br />And yeah I was thinking of changing speed in the middle of a song, so that in one part I could do strait notes and another I could do triplets for example. But I'll wait until I get more basics before I tackle that.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
